    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it's just not that simple. i see the look on their faces when they have to come over just to help me with the basics. it breaks my heart. i've always been the one taking care of everyone else, and now i'm just... taking. it feels like the most selfless thing would be to just stop being a weight around their necks. wouldn't it be easier for everyone if i wasn't even here to worry about?",
