      "content": "but that's just putting it on them again... forcing them to manage my feelings and my \"boundaries\" just adds more to their plate. they already spend so much time worrying about my health. if i just wasn't around to be a constant problem, they could finally just live their lives without this shadow hanging over them. it feels less like a problem and more like a gift to them, honestly. like, wouldn't they be more free if they didn't have to carry me anymore?",
